{
  "texts": [
    "The predominant applications of chatbots were for information retrieval and assistance with proofreading or translation (Table 1).",
    "Furthermore, chatbots were notably employed in the academic domain, particularly for initial drafting and editing of the manuscripts.",
    "More than half of the respondents reported saving 1 to 5",
    "working hours per week as a result of using the chatbot applications.",
    "A subgroup analysis focusing on pathologists who applied LLMs in their academic work revealed that the primary application was in writing the introduction and abstract sections, with 24 and 23 participants utilizing LLMs for these parts, respectively."
  ]
}